member.remarks:
Learning problem. Given some training observation sequences O = {o1, o2, ..., oK}
and general structure of HMM (numbers of hidden and visible states), determine
HMM parameters M = (A, B, pi) that best fit training data.

Learning problem. Given some training observation sequences O = {o1, o2, ..., oK}
and general structure of HMM (numbers of hidden and visible states), determine
HMM parameters M = (A, B, pi) that best fit training data.

